We initiate a BUY rating on Grand Banks Yachts with a target price of S$0.50  pegged to 10.2x FY23F P/E (25% discount to peers average P/E of 13.6x)  representing a potential upside of 49%. Backed by an all-time high order book  Grand Banks remains well-positioned to benefit from the buoyant luxury boat market that has enjoyed strong pandemic-led demand.Bigger and premium models  improving operational efficiencies and the favourable USD/MYR exchange rate will drive margins upwards. Like luxury watches  GBY offers timeless  classic designs that retain old customers and attract new ones. Ex-cash P/E of 2x implies a payback period of only 2 years  rendering Grand Banks a very attractive takeover or privatisation candidate in the not too distant future.
